title: Dm2 Mixman Mixer Software
description:
This is original software Cd image and updates for the Dm2 mixman mixer.

The original Cd was only for win98.
The updated for Xp are included.

Instructions: burn or mount the iso file with original software disk.

then click on the 1.1 update file. You must have the disk in to run the update.

then update using 1.2 file after that. Should be it.

Enjoy.
